  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bcd: \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I will quit if quota not withdrawn: Speaker",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "If President Gotabaya Rajapaksa does not resign from the presidency, then he will resign from the post of Speaker, said Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardana in the ongoing special meeting of party leaders."
      ],
